# Exclude local build artifacts and dependencies from the Docker build context.
# The Dockerfile copies only specific source paths (gradle build files, api/src,
# client-spec), so these directories are never needed inside the build and only
# bloat the upload context and risk stale-artifact cache invalidation.
.git/
.github/
.gradle/
build/
**/build/
node_modules/
**/node_modules/
clients/
*.log
